Interface news.
界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：IRNA“ 在库姆等什叶派圣城，出现了朝圣者亲吻甚至舔清真寺门墙的情况。
Source: IRNA "In Shiite holy cities such as Qom, there have been cases of pilgrims kissing and even licking mosque gates.
部分宗教领袖认为库姆等地的清真寺有治愈疾病的作用，甚至呼吁朝圣者反抗防疫措施。
Some religious leaders believe mosques in places like Qom have a healing effect, even calling on pilgrims to resist vaccination efforts.
”伊朗卫生部3月4日统计显示，伊朗新增新冠肺炎病例586例，新增死亡病例15例。
Iran has 586 new cases of pneumonia and 15 new deaths, the Health Ministry said Monday.
截至当地时间4日中午，伊朗共确诊新冠肺炎病例2922例，其中552例康复，92例死亡。
By noon local time Thursday, Iran had confirmed 2,922 new cases of pneumonia, of which 552 had recovered and 92 had died.
据阿拉比亚电视台报道，此前有伊朗媒体称工业、矿业和贸易部长拉哈马尼（Reza Rahmani）确诊新冠肺炎，目前正在德黑兰一所医院的ICU病房救治。
The news follows Iranian media reports that Reza Rahmani, the minister of industry, mining and trade, confirmed pneumonia and is being treated in an ICU ward at a Tehran hospital.
但工业部有官员否认该说法，称拉哈马尼并未感染新冠病毒，而是因两伊战争中的“化学性损伤”接受治疗。
But officials at the Ministry of Industry denied the claim, saying Rahamani had not been infected with the new Crown virus, but had been treated for "chemical damage" in the Iran-Iraq war.
自疫情爆发以来，伊朗政界已有多名官员被确诊感染，包括副总统埃卜特卡尔和紧急卫生服务部负责人。
Since the outbreak, a number of Iranian political officials have been diagnosed with the infection, including Vice-President Ebtkar and the head of the Emergency Health Service.
截至3日，伊朗议会有23名成员被确诊，占议员总数的8%。
As at 3 March, 23 members of the Iranian Parliament had been confirmed, representing 8 per cent of the total number of members.
议会副议长梅斯里（Abdolreza Mesri）已呼吁各议员暂时不要与民众接触。
Abdolreza Mesri, deputy speaker of parliament, has called on lawmakers to stay away from the public.
伊朗总统府官网4日消息说，该国总统鲁哈尼表示，新冠病毒疫情的暴发几乎已经影响了伊朗所有省份。
President Rowhani says the outbreak of the new crown virus has affected almost all Iranian provinces, officials said Thursday.
随着疫情持续扩散，伊朗最高领袖哈梅内伊周二发表讲话，要求各部门全力配合卫生部的工作并呼吁民众遵守疫情防护规定。
As the epidemic continues to spread, Iran's Supreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei issued a speech Tuesday calling on all ministries to cooperate fully with the health ministry and calling on the people to abide by the epidemic's rules.
哈梅内伊称，“真主让我们对自己和他人的健康负责”，帮助阻止疫情扩散的行为是“好事”，任何助长其扩散的行为则是“罪恶”。
According to Khamenei, "Allah makes us responsible for our own health and that of others," helping to stop the spread of the epidemic is "good," and any act that contributes to its spread is "evil."
最近几日，在库姆等什叶派圣城，出现了朝圣者亲吻甚至舔清真寺门墙的情况，以试图证明宗教场所对病毒免疫。
In recent days, in Shiite holy cities such as Qom, pilgrims have been kissing and even licking mosque gates in an attempt to prove that religious sites are immune to the virus.
部分宗教领袖认为库姆等地的清真寺有治愈疾病的作用，甚至呼吁朝圣者反抗防疫措施。
Some religious leaders believe mosques in places like Qom have a healing effect, even calling on pilgrims to resist vaccination efforts.
周二，两名男子因在网上发布舔清真寺门墙的视频被警方逮捕。
Two men were arrested Tuesday for posting videos of licking the mosque's door wall.
上周，沙特阿拉伯已宣布暂时禁止朝圣者前往圣城麦加和麦地那。
Last week, Saudi Arabia announced a temporary ban on pilgrims travelling to the holy cities of Mecca and Medina.
但伊朗的库姆等地依然有大量朝圣者，清真寺还在正常开放。
But there are still large numbers of pilgrims in places like Qom in Iran, and mosques are still open normally.
已经有民众在网上呼吁什叶派各最高宗教学者大阿亚图拉介入，防止清真寺成为交叉感染之地。
There has been a popular online call for the intervention of Grand Ayatollah, the most senior Shi'ite religious scholar, to prevent mosques from becoming places of cross-infection.
哈梅内伊也是大阿亚图拉。
Khamenei is also the Grand Ayatollah.
据界面新闻此前报道，为控制疫情，伊朗多座城市正在紧急建设收治新冠病毒感染者的传染病院。
Interface News previously reported that in order to control the epidemic, many cities in Iran are emergency construction of the new crown virus patients admitted to the infectious diseases hospital.
在中部城市亚兹德，政府承诺将在数日内建成一座占地1000平方米的医院。
In the central city of Yazd, the government has pledged to build a 1,000-square-metre hospital within days.
在库姆，伊斯兰革命卫队也建起了一所野战医院。
In Qom, the Islamic Revolutionary Guard Corps also built a field hospital.
伊朗食品和药品管理局则宣布，药店将不得继续出售防护性口罩，口罩将通过政府机构免费向民众发放。
Iran's Food and Drug Administration has announced that pharmacies will no longer be allowed to sell protective masks, which will be distributed to the public free of charge through government agencies.
遭遇疫情的省份将优先获得口罩。
Preference will be given to obtaining masks in provinces affected by the epidemic.
伊朗负责科技事务的副总统萨他瑞（Sorena Sattari）称，目前伊朗每天的口罩产量在20万只左右，之后还会上升到每天30万只。
According to Sorena Sattari, Iran's vice president for science and technology, Iran now produces about 200,000 masks a day and will grow to 300,000 a day thereafter.
德黑兰巴基亚塔莱医科大学则于周三宣布开始对一种草药和一种喷剂进行临床试验。
Tehran's Bakiatalai Medical University on Wednesday announced the start of clinical trials of a herbal medicine and a sprayer.
校长贾拉里（Ali-Reza Jalali）表示，这两种药物并非专门用于治疗新冠病毒的药物，而是帮助患者更快恢复的辅助性药物。
The headmaster, Ali-Reza Jalali, said the two drugs were not drugs specifically designed to treat the new crown virus, but complementary drugs to help patients recover faster.
从临床试验到获得上市许可，至少需要两到三个月。
It takes at least two to three months from clinical trials to getting a listing license.
